<br>
Using the pet go away/reclaim trick, the toon you're PLing doesn't have to finish off the mob.  You can have the toon being PL'ed get some nukes melee/in early, then you get rid of pet when mob is near death, summon next pet and have that pet finish it off (use earth pet for the root).  I found that as long as the second pet didn't do more damage than the toon being leveled, everything was fine.  Your mage can also do some damage, but mage plus current pet can't outdamage your cleric.<br>
